steps.html_instructions: Head west on E Rosser Ave toward N 5th St

Slight right onto I-94BUS W/W Main Ave
Continue to follow I-94BUS W
Take the exit on the left onto I-94 W

Turn left onto US-85 S/1st Ave SW/Theodore Roosevelt Expressway
Continue to follow US-85 S
Entering South Dakota

Turn right to merge onto I-90 W
Entering Wyoming

Turn right onto US-18 W/US-20 W/W 8th St
Continue to follow US-18 W/US-20 W

Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-25 S/US-87 S/Cheyenne and merge onto I-25 S/US-87 S
Continue to follow I-25 S
Passing through Colorado
Entering New Mexico
Turn right onto NM-466 N/Old Pecos Trail (signs for Historic US 66)
